- **Modern Browsers**: Chrome 60+, Firefox 55+, Safari 11+, Edge 79+
- **Mobile**: iOS Safari 11+, Chrome Mobile 60+
- **Graceful Degradation**: Basic functionality in older browsers

## Performance Targets
- **Load Time**: < 1 second on 3G connection
- **Bundle Size**: < 100KB total (uncompressed)
- **API Response**: Cached responses for improved UX
- **Responsive**: Works smoothly on all device sizes

## Security Considerations
- **Input Validation**: Client-side email format validation
- **HTTPS Redirects**: Ensure all redirects use HTTPS
- **CORS Handling**: Proper error handling for cross-origin requests
- **No Sensitive Data**: No storage of user emails or personal information

## Deployment Requirements
- **CPanel Compatibility**: Standard shared hosting with file manager
- **No Server Dependencies**: Pure client-side application
- **Upload Process**: Direct file upload to public_html or subdirectory
- **Domain Setup**: Works with any domain/subdomain configuration

